GONNA CHARM ME...

00:35.456 --> 00:38.958
WHERE'S DANI? WE ALL WROTE THE BIRTHDAY SONG
TOGETHER, WE ALL HAVE TO SING IT TO HIM.

00:38.959 --> 00:41.422
I'LL INVITE HER. YO, DANI!

00:42.713 --> 00:46.836
WHAT? IN MY FAMILY, THAT'S
A FORMAL INVITATION.

00:46.837 --> 00:50.380
