01:57.288 --> 02:00.740
- OH. GOOD, WHAT DO I DO?
- WE'RE GONNA CALL HIM.

02:00.741 --> 02:02.582
ON THE PHONE.

02:02.583 --> 02:04.043
BUT THEN I WON'T
BE ABLE TO SEE HIM

02:04.044 --> 02:07.377
AND WITNESS THAT MOMENT WHEN HE
TRANSITIONS FROM BOY TO MAN.

02:07.378 --> 02:09.249
YEAH, HONEY, I THINK
THAT'S ALREADY HAPPENED,

02:09.250 --> 02:12.922
AND LUCKILY WE WEREN'T
THERE TO WITNESS THAT.

02:12.923 --> 02:14.924
LOOK, I KNOW IT'S A
BIG DEAL TO YOU.

02:14.925 --> 02:17.096
IT'S HIS BIRTHDAY, BUT WE CAN
JUST CALL HIM ON THE PHONE.

02:17.097 --> 02:18.678
THAT'S JUST AS GOOD
AS A VIDEO CALL.

02:18.679 --> 02:21.891
YOU'RE RIGHT. A
PHONE CALL IS FINE.

02:21.892 --> 02:24.974
I'M SORRY. GIVE ME A
KISS, YOU BIG STUD.

02:24.975 --> 02:28.568
- MM...
- OR MAYBE I'LL JUST WAVE.

02:28.569 --> 02:31.030
AND MAYBE INSTEAD OF SEX,
WE CAN JUST HIGH FIVE.

02:31.031 --> 02:34.274
HONEY, HONEY. LOOK, I KNOW
HOW MUCH THIS MEANS TO YOU.

02:34.275 --> 02:35.905
BUT WE TRIED. I TRIED SKYPE.

02:35.906 --> 02:38.117
I TRIED FACETIME. I DON'T
KNOW WHAT ELSE TO DO.

02:38.118 --> 02:41.201
YOU KNOW WHAT? OKAY.
MAYBE IT'S THE ROUTER.

02:41.202 --> 02:42.952
YOU KNOW WHAT? I'LL UNPLUG
IT, WE CAN RESET IT.

02:42.953 --> 02:44.994
WE'LL SEE WHAT HAPPENS. IT SHOULD
TAKE, LIKE, THREE MINUTES.

02:44.995 --> 02:48.047
