ARE WE GONNA DO FOR THREE MINUTES?

02:48.048 --> 02:52.712
WE COULD HARD BOIL
AN EGG, OR, UH...

02:52.713 --> 02:55.425
YOU KNOW, WE COULD
HAVE SOME SEX.

02:55.426 --> 02:59.009
IS IT JUST ME, OR SINCE MARRIAGE
HAS YOUR GAME GONE WAY DOWNHILL?

02:59.930 --> 03:02.302
LENNOX, CAN I GET
A LITTLE ADVICE?

03:02.303 --> 03:04.354
WAIT, YOU'RE ASKING
ME FOR ADVICE?

03:04.355 --> 03:07.897
YOU GREW UP ON THE ROAD WITH ROCK BANDS.
I THOUGHT YOU KNEW EVERYTHING.

03:07.898 --> 03:11.190
I KNOW WHAT GENE SIMMONS
LOOKS LIKE IN SPANX,

03:11.191 --> 03:15.024
