05:32.042 --> 05:34.714
WHY DON'T WE JUST GET SOME CANDLES
AND STICK THEM IN SOME DOG POO?

05:34.715 --> 05:36.876
'CAUSE THAT'S THE SAME
THING AS CAKE, RIGHT?

05:36.877 --> 05:39.419
HEY, RYDER WILL EAT
ALMOST ANYTHING.

05:39.420 --> 05:42.962
OKAY, WE ARE NOT DOING
THIS BY PHONE, OR BY TEXT.

05:42.963 --> 05:46.095
WE'RE GONNA BE TALKING TO OUR LOVED
ONE ON THE BIG COMPUTER SCREEN,

05:46.096 --> 05:50.229
ALL OF US, FACE TO VIRTUAL FACE!
ANY QUESTIONS?

05:50.230 --> 05:51.432
THE ANSWER IS "NO."

05:52.893 --> 05:54.564
