THE PROBLEM IS. HA!

05:54.565 --> 05:56.105
I JUST NEED TO UPDATE
OUR OPERATING SYSTEM.

05:56.106 --> 05:57.737
HOW LONG WILL THAT TAKE?

05:57.738 --> 06:00.069
FASTER THAN A NERD CAN GET
HERE IN A SMART CAR, BABY.

06:00.070 --> 06:01.611
(beeping)

06:01.612 --> 06:03.903
THERE WE GO. ALL RIGHT,
DOWNLOAD WILL BE COMPLETE IN...

06:03.904 --> 06:05.785
FIVE MINUTES. YOU'RE WELCOME.

06:05.786 --> 06:07.156
- (computer beeps)
- OH. THREE MINUTES.

06:07.157 --> 06:08.448
YEAH. I'M AWESOME.

06:08.449 --> 06:10.159
- (beeps)
- TWELVE MINUTES.

06:10.160 --> 06:13.453
- UM... TWO HOURS.
- (beeping)

06:13.454 --> 06:16.586
- 300 HOURS? -HOW IS IT GOING UP?
JOE, DO SOMETHING!

06:16.587 --> 06:19.839
I'M TRYING! ABORT, ABORT! INTERRUPT SCRIPT!
HOLD ON! WAIT A MINUTE! OH!

06:19.840 --> 06:22.502
HEY! I GOT IT. OKAY. I
JUST STOPPED THE DOWNLOAD!

06:22.503 --> 06:24.554
- (laughs) -WELL,
CONGRATULATIONS, JACK BAUER.

06:24.555 --> 06:26.005
AND THIS HELPS US HOW?

06:26.006 --> 06:27.967
HOW? BECAUSE NOW WE DEFINITELY
KNOW IT'S THE ROUTER, HONEY.

06:27.968 --> 06:31.892
AND IF THERE'S ONE THING I
KNOW ABOUT ROUTERS, IT'S...

06:33.604 --> 06:35.605
ROUTERS. TRUST ME.

06:35.606 --> 06:37.938
OF COURSE I TRUST YOU.

06:38.939 --> 06:40.359
HELLO, JIFFY NERDS?

06:40.360 --> 06:42.071
I NEED YOU RIGHT NOW.
MY NAME IS...

06:42.072 --> 06:45.194
YOU ALREADY KNOW MY NAME?
AND MY ADDRESS?

06:45.195 --> 06:47.868
WOW, YOU GUYS ARE GOOD.

06:52.583 --> 06:56.496
(air hissing)

06:56.497 --> 06:59.839
WOW. LOOKS LIKE SOMEBODY THREW A
TEENY-TINY HAND GRENADE AT YOUR ROUTER.

06:59.840 --> 07:03.132
YEAH, WELL, YOU KNOW, DUST CAN REALLY
FOUL UP FRAGILE EQUIPMENT LIKE THIS.

07:03.133 --> 07:05.505
SO, UH, I SHOULD HAVE US
UP AND RUNNING VERY SOON.

07:05.506 --> 07:07.346
THAT IS ONE THING I'M SURE OF.

07:07.347 --> 07:08.508
BECAUSE OF WHAT
YOU'RE DOING HERE.

07:08.509 --> 07:10.389
I'M SO LUCKY TO HAVE YOU.

07:10.390 --> 07:13.052
YOU KNOW, A MAN IS NOTHING WITHOUT
A GOOD WOMAN RIGHT BY HIS SIDE.

07:13.053 --> 07:15.725
OH, AND THAT'S WHERE I AM.
RIGHT HERE BY YOUR SIDE.

07:15.726 --> 07:17.898
- (doorbell rings)
- GOTTA GO!

07:23.614 --> 07:27.827
YOU CALLED. WE HEARD. YOUR PROBLEM
WILL BE CURED. I'M A JIFFY NERD.

07:27.828 --> 07:30.329
OH, GOOD, YOU'RE HERE. THANK YOU
FOR COMING AROUND THE BACK.

07:30.330 --> 07:32.703
NO PROB. (grunts)

07:34.835 --> 07:36.786
WE'RE TRYING TO MAKE A VIDEO
CALL AND IT'S NOT WORKING

07:36.787 --> 07:38.788
AND MY HUSBAND THINKS
HE CAN FIX IT HIMSELF.

07:38.789 --> 07:41.420
OH, WE GET THAT ALL THE TIME.
IN FACT, MOST OF OUR BUSINESS

07:41.421 --> 07:43.543
IS HUSBANDS FIXING THINGS.

07:43.544 --> 07:45.845
HAS IT BEEN THROWN AGAINST
A WALL IN FRUSTRATION YET?

07:45.846 --> 07:47.967
MY HUSBAND OR THE COMPUTER?

07:47.968 --> 07:50.009
THEY'RE BOTH FINE. FOR NOW.

07:50.010 --> 07:51.971
- UH, WHERE'S THE COMPUTER?
- IN THE LIVING ROOM.

07:51.972 --> 07:53.803
- OKAY. -WHOA! WHERE DO
YOU THINK YOU'RE GOING?

07:53.804 --> 07:57.016
I FIND IT HELPS IF I'M IN THE
SAME ROOM AS THE MACHINE.

07:57.017 --> 07:59.188
I JUST WANT TO VIDEO
CHAT WITH MY NEPHEW.

07:59.189 --> 08:00.810
TODAY IS HIS
EIGHTEENTH BIRTHDAY.

08:00.811 --> 08:02.522
AT LEAST FOR ANOTHER 23 MINUTES.

08:02.523 --> 08:04.734
AND YOU WANT TO BE ABLE TO TALK
TO HIM ON HIS ACTUAL BIRTHDAY.

08:04.735 --> 08:06.866
THANK YOU!

08:06.867 --> 08:09.278
WE HAD A CONNECTION FOR A SECOND,
BUT THEN THE SCREEN FROZE.

08:09.279 --> 08:11.662
- WHAT DID IT LOOK LIKE?
- LIKE THIS.

08:13.283 --> 08:15.575
NO, I MEAN WAS THE
IMAGE PIXILATED?

08:15.576 --> 08:17.997
WAS IT JUST BLACK? I SHOULD
REALLY SEE WHAT'S ON THE DISPLAY.

08:17.998 --> 08:19.879
NO PROBLEM. I'LL BE RIGHT BACK.

08:19.880 --> 08:22.461
MA'AM? IT'S COLD OUT HERE.

08:22.462 --> 08:24.924
WHAT? YOU MUST BE ANEMIC,
IT'S LIKE A SAUNA OUT HERE.

08:24.925 --> 08:27.047
JUST WARM YOURSELF ON
THE DRYER EXHAUST.

08:30.761 --> 08:33.803
LOOK AT YOU, FIXING A COMPUTER.
CAN I GET A PICTURE?

08:33.804 --> 08:36.015
OF ME FIXING THE COMPUTER?

08:36.016 --> 08:37.727
WELL, IN THE OLD
DAYS A MAN WOULD BE

08:37.728 --> 08:39.769
RAISING A BARN OR
KILLING A BEAR.

08:39.770 --> 08:42.902
THESE ARE THE MOMENTS
WOMEN CHERISH.

08:42.903 --> 08:44.815
KNOCK YOURSELF OUT, BABE.

08:46.857 --> 08:48.237
WHAT ARE YOU...
YOU WANNA TAKE...

08:48.238 --> 08:50.820
(camera shutter clicks)

08:50.821 --> 08:53.033
YOU KNOW, YOU DON'T HAVE TO
BE IN EVERY PICTURE YOU TAKE.

08:54.494 --> 08:55.956
HONEY.

08:57.998 --> 09:00.750
- (door slams) -HERE YOU
GO, EVERYTHING YOU NEED.

09:00.751 --> 09:03.292
- FIX IT.
- IT'S A PHOTO OF YOU.

09:03.293 --> 09:06.926
- THERE'S A COMPUTER THERE, TOO.
- I CAN'T DO ANYTHING WITH THIS.

09:06.927 --> 09:09.929
SHOULD I EVEN ASK IF I CAN
SCAN THE COMPUTER FOR VIRUSES?

09:09.930 --> 09:14.724
(sighs) PRESS CONTROL, F7 AND THAT
WILL RUN THE BUILT-IN ANTIVIRUS SCAN.

09:14.725 --> 09:16.556
I'M ALL OVER IT.

09:18.729 --> 09:21.560
MEL, CHECK IT OUT. I
HARD-WIRED THE ROUTER.

09:21.561 --> 09:23.182
SO WE SHOULD HAVE
A PERFECT SIGNAL.

09:23.183 --> 09:25.775
- YOU FIXED IT? -WELL, YEAH.
BUT I'LL KNOW FOR SURE

09:25.776 --> 09:27.947
AS SOON AS I'M DONE
REINSTALLING VIDEO CHAT.

09:27.948 --> 09:30.690
OH. OKAY. WELL, IN THE MEANTIME
HOW ABOUT I JUST REACH IN HERE

09:30.691 --> 09:35.865
- AND PRESS CONTROL, F7.
- WAIT, WAIT! CONTROL, F7?

09:35.866 --> 09:38.077
WHAT ARE YOU INSINUATING?
THAT MY COMPUTER HAS A VIRUS?

09:38.078 --> 09:40.620
OF COURSE NOT!

09:40.621 --> 09:43.082
I KEEP MY COMPUTER CLEAN, MEL.

09:43.083 --> 09:45.965
I GOTTA TELL YOU
SOMETHING, I'M SHOCKED,

09:45.966 --> 09:47.506
AND A LITTLE HURT.

09:47.507 --> 09:49.920
YOU'RE RIGHT. I'M SORRY.

09:51.341 --> 09:53.633
BACK, BACK, BACK, BACK OFF!
ALL RIGHT, LOOK.

09:53.634 --> 09:56.095
YOU EITHER TRUST ME ON THIS OR
YOU DON'T TRUST ME ON THIS.

09:56.096 --> 09:58.768
WELL, IF THOSE ARE MY
ONLY TWO OPTIONS, THEN...

09:58.769 --> 10:01.061
I TRUST YOU. (laughs)

10:06.106 --> 10:09.568
I WAS HOPING THE MEMORY
OF HEAT WOULD WARM ME.

10:09.569 --> 10:11.991
HE WOULDN'T LET ME TOUCH THE COMPUTER.
WHAT DO YOU USUALLY DO NEXT?

10:11.992 --> 10:13.033
COME INSIDE.

10:17.497 --> 10:20.409
- HEY, DANI.
- Dani: HM?

10:20.410 --> 10:22.371
YOU KNOW, UNTIL YOU CAME ALONG,

10:22.372 --> 10:24.043
